patthana8.29:1.1_0: Naganthañceva naaganthaniyañca dhammaṁ paṭicca nagantho ceva naaganthaniyo ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana8.29:1.1_1: Naganthañceva naaganthaniyañca dhammaṁ paṭicca naaganthaniyo ceva nano ca gantho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana8.29:1.1_2: Naganthañceva naaganthaniyañca dhammaṁ paṭicca nagantho ceva naaganthaniyo ca naaganthaniyo ceva nano ca gantho ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.
patthana8.29:2.1_0: Naaganthaniyañceva nano ca ganthaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naaganthaniyo ceva nanogantho ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana8.29:2.1_1: Naaganthaniyañceva nano ca ganthaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nagantho ceva naaganthaniyo ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana8.29:2.1_2: Naaganthaniyañceva nano ca ganthaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nagantho ceva naaganthaniyo ca naaganthaniyo ceva nano ca gantho ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.
patthana8.29:3.1_0: Naganthañceva naaganthaniyañca naaganthaniyañceva nano ca ganthañca dhammaṁ paṭicca nagantho ceva naaganthaniyo ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana8.29:4.1_0: Hetuyā nava …pe… vipāke ekaṁ …pe… avigate nava. (Sabbattha vitthāro.)
